main event: A series of unidentified flying objects were reported over Pennington, NJ involving sightings of civilian saucers.
interesting points: The sightings involved 3 civilian saucers observed traveling together., The objects were described as disc-shaped and shiny., Witnesses included a commercial airline pilot and military personnel., The first sighting was reported at approximately 2:45 AM and lasted for about 2 minutes., The objects exhibited unusual speed and maneuverability.
witness description: A commercial airline pilot and military personnel from Brookley AFB.
